// Import
import Vue from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import VueRouter from 'vue-router'
import router from './router'
import animated from 'animate.css'

// Use
Vue.use(VueRouter)
Vue.use(animated)

Vue.config.productionTip = false

new Vue({
  router,
  render: h => h(App),
  store
}).$mount('#app')
